Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,a boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,an island with two parts, one \Nburning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After learning about Caesar's motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they are on the move to save the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,kidnap Caesar, and escape from the island--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,all while trying to escape Shinokuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have treated him\N as my young brother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and watched closely\N over him as he grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard for you, Vergo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need you to take care of Law there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna make him wish\N that he was never born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So kill him in a horrific way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Luffy Dies from Exposure?!\N The Spine-chilling Snow Woman Monet!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:39.36,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}D BUILDING - THE "SAD" MANUFACTURING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like my hand has been bitten
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,by my own dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,even for a mischievous child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You were too smart\N for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,People like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...tend to die young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be easiest for me to kill \Nyou by crushing your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll torment you slowly as I please
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and warp your smart-ass face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too soon to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:31.47,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}C BUILDING 4TH FLOOR - CAESAR'S RESEARCH ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! What does she want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bird woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go after the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing again! But it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Another wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...Jet Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these walls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bird woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten-layer Kamakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ten layers to this Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to break the snow walls
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if they're layered one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you trying to buy time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can break them all quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can break this Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think so, stop wasting my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm gonna lose you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I will win\N if I fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the strongest isn't always\N the winner in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a block of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't push me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're now in my embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and your power is diminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You will lose all of\N your physical strength
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to my cold body in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,your heart will freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,die in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing heavily around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel very tired, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the beginning\N of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What tremendous hidden strength he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But falling through here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,will land him in the slide to the \Ngarbage dump deep underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll never be able to come \Nback up unless he can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect him to\N sabotage himself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.80,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}B BUILDING 3RD FLOOR - NEAR THE BISCUIT ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never\N eat that candy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard\N but you have to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go to the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in our way,\N you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop them without hurting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The effect of the Rumble Ball\N is about to wear off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We can eat the candy soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! To the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can eat the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take more of the drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it will ruin your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't save them\N because I have no power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Chopper-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with those kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They've gotten more violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us what's going on, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar is trying to turn them into giants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to make them demonic \Nsoldiers, just as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't handle them alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have to stop them\N as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Biscuit Room is to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The candies are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha is the only child in her \Nright mind and she's helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We were trying to stop the other children
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but we couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She is protecting the candies\N in the room all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here at the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mil Fleurs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forward while I hold them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not gonna be\N stopped so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll stop at nothing\N when they're in that state!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's evil candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We asked Chopper-chan and\N the others to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't listen to them,\N we can't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! That's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna eat it all yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let them have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home with everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold! I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit is sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\N worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Monet-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the bird woman\N that I told you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Monet-san, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha, it's not nice\N to keep it all to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to share\N the candies with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she uses sorcery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Logia-type?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's our enemy, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Monet-san, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.87,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1)}B BUILDING 2ND FLOOR - AN EXAMINATION ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where did the boy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He entered into the "secret room"\N where no one is allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and transformed into a small dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy named Momonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The brat who transformed into a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, "the boy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\N about that, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching it secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened in the "secret room"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so I didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I got here on the same ship \Nwith him so I've been worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This laboratory is big and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...there are various treatment rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's just in a different room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he eating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't he eat anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, he's eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone about him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the "secret room." Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe one of the\N children knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to let the Master know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd come to this secret room myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the only place I can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all their fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It could've been a great show - \Neverything perfect and lovely,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and more befitting of the\N world's greatest scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But they screwed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy G-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make them regret ruining my plan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,even after they go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow down to my scientific prowess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys frustrated because your \Nscheme is coming crashing down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that important to you guys, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth, you squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to me, my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Counter Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message from Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "What a shame."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was pretty sure that I could \Ntake my heart back from Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't expect you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vergo-san to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have to be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to silence\N you anyway, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You better make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so pleasant to watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...a scumbag like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:22:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirate -
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker's rage explodes at the fact \Nthat Vergo's betrayed his men,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and Vergo closes in on him \Nwith overwhelming Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The fierce battle between Smoker and Vergo intensifies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as Smoker puts his spirit and \Npride as a Marine on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fists Collide!\N A Battle of the Two Vice Admirals!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
